      "text": "Yes, you know, during the part that we just came back from, I was asked or told I should put full emotions into my comments that I'm making.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I would like to make some comments on it, if I may.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You know, when I am asked by many people, how did you survive, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I have a basic answer.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And that also will relate why I'm not so emotional when I relate my [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] past, the history of my survival.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that stock comment basically is [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] it's a long story, but if you want to put it in a nutshell, on how I survived, I would have to say, you have to picture [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a 5,000 mile minefield.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it's a road that's 5,000 miles long, with mines every foot and a half, three feet wide.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In quick succession, minute after minute, hour after hour, day after day, week after week, month after month, and year after year.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that is how I can say how I survived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because each minute, each hour, each day is a new and different dangerous episode.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And naturally, the youth helped you not to become so emotional over many of the aspects and the areas that-- of your suffering, let's say, and suffering with that.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to think back, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] some of the rare and unusual episodes that takes guts and finesse, in plain language, chutzpah.",
      "word_count": 28
